  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1054">
<l>irattalu mītalē pōluṅ karattal</l>
<l>kaṉavilun tēṟṟātār māṭṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To beg of such as never think of withholding (their charity) even in their dreams, is in fact the same as giving (it oneself);</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
